# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Publish-list: git ignores EVERYTHING by default, then re-includes
# only the real live-app files below. This means deploy.bat can
# never accidentally publish the planning docs, the aiAssist draft,
# backups, or other local-only files.
# To publish a NEW file later, add a matching "!/filename" line.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/*

!/.gitignore
!/index.html
!/manifest.json
!/CNAME
!/README.md
!/sw.js
!/icon-32.png
!/icon-180.png
!/icon-192.png
!/icon-512.png
!/icon-maskable-512.png
